CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1961, pg. 20 reads: "Lucky Boys And Girls winners of annual drawing which gives everyone a chance to win a prize."
TitMainTitle: Group of young boys and girls holding basketballs, footballs, flashlights, and board games, gathered on field in South Park for the annual Pittsburgh Courier Newsboys' Picnic
